Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.86,0:00:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.15,0:00:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你都有那隻蜥蜴幫你回復了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.02,0:00:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,,{\fad(400,400)\fs36\fnMSungHK-Bold\bord0\shad2}2024年2月23日 第35層 迷途之森
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.23,0:00:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒必要分配回復水晶給你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.86,0:00:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.31,0:00:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都沒怎麼衝上前線 還需要用到水晶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.16,0:00:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不像小偶像西莉卡妹妹那樣有眾男士幫忙回復
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們兩個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.81,0:00:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要什麼道具了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.87,0:00:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會再和你組隊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.01,0:00:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要我的團隊可是多不勝數呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.64,0:00:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下 西莉卡妹妹

Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:53.70,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}認めてた臆病な過去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.06,0:01:01.77,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}分からないままに怖がってた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:03.89,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}後ろの自分が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.97,0:01:10.72,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}現実を今に映す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.83,0:01:15.83,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}いくつもの空を描いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:17.89,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}ここはきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.20,0:01:23.37,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}儚い心 乱して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.59,0:01:29.08,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}夢で高く飛んだ躰は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:31.94,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}どんな不安纏っても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.10,0:01:33.98,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}振り払ってく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.31,0:01:38.42,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}眠る小さな想い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.67,0:01:40.64,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}広がりだして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:42.70,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}気づく 弱い 私
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.84,0:01:49.40,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}君がいれば 暗い世界 強くいれた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:55.16,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}長い夢見る心は そう 永遠で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.77,0:01:59.27,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I wanna always stay with you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:04.87,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I give you everything I have

Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:53.70,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}正視著膽怯的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.06,0:01:01.77,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}依然無法理解地畏懼著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:03.89,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}背後的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.97,0:01:10.72,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}此刻映照在現實中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.83,0:01:15.83,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}描繪了數片天空的此處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:17.89,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}一定是在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.20,0:01:23.37,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}亂我脆弱心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.59,0:01:29.08,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}乘著夢想高飛身軀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:31.94,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}無論有任何不安糾纏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.10,0:01:33.98,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}都掙脫前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.31,0:01:38.42,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}將沉睡著的小小的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.67,0:01:40.64,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}擴展開來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:42.70,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}意識到弱小的我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.84,0:01:49.40,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}只要有你在 黑暗的世界 也能一直堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:55.16,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}用沉眠許久的心 永遠堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.77,0:01:59.27,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I wanna always stay with you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:04.87,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I give you everything I have

